extends layout.pug

block header
	div(class="jumbotron necc-jumbo mbr-jumbo p-3 p-md-5 text-white")
		div(class="col-md-6 px-0")
			h1(class="display-3") Membership
			p(class="lead my-3") Did you know? There is a thriving Clemson community right here in New England. We would love for you to be a part of it! Join us or renew your membership today for just $25.

block content
	div(class="row")
		h1(class="mt-2") About Membership
		p(class="lead") The New England Clemson Club (NECC)  is part of a network of regional clubs within the U.S. that are affiliated with the Clemson Alumni Association. The dues paid to the Club help provide the financial resources and support needed to host football game watches, networking events, social events like our annual accepted student send-off party, and more!

		p(class="lead") In addition, to help make our events possible, as an NECC member, you can take advantage of all the other great benefits of membership such as advanced access to sporting event tickets, early-bird ticket prices, food specials at events, and free NECC swag. Become a member today!

		h3 Benefits Include:
	div(class="row")
		ul(class="mb-4") 
			li Access to NECC block tickets for the Clemson vs. Boston College game (when @ Boston College)
			li Food specials at game viewing parties
			li Advanced ticket purchases
			li Early bird ticket prices	
			li Invitations/Access to Members-Only events
			li Raffles
			li Networking events
			li Free NECC swag

	div(class="row")
		div(class="col-md-12")
			h5(class="text-center mbr-notice") Please Note: Currently there are no offers, see you all next football season!

	div(class="row")
		div(class="col-md-5 text-center mbr-signup rounded")
			h3 Already a member?
			small(text="text-muted") Event tickets and other member-only benefits can be accessed below.
			div(class="col-md-12")
				a(class="btn btn-clemson mt-3" href="/members") Log in


		div(class="col-md-5 text-center mbr-signup rounded")
			h3 Sign up for Membership
			small(text="text-muted") $25.00 for an annual membership. 
			div(class="col-md-12")
				div(class="mt-3" id="paypal-button")
					script(src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/api/checkout.js" type="text/javascript")
					script(src="scripts/paypal.js" type="text/javascript")

	div(class="row")
		div(class="col-md-12")
			h2(class="mt-5") Stay in Touch with Clemson University!
			p(class="lead mb-0") Interested in recieving email from Clemson? You can use the form below to add or update your information.
			small Please note, this mailing list is handled by Clemson University, not by the the New England Alumni Assoc.
			div
				a(class="btn btn-clemson mt-3" href="https://cualumni.clemson.edu/bio-update") Clemson Newsletter

	hr(class="featurette-divider")
block scripts
